description: Team Blue Pulled ahead at the end of round 2 with 1080 points to red's 1031. Blue learned to use their tags wisely and Red is paying the price for it. The rookies are holding their own on the mats against the veterans and with each other. Never in the history of Ultimate Surrender have two rookies come in their first tag team matches and shown so much skill, determination and heart. The is an exciting match up and the score is dead even up until the final minute of this exciting round 3.
title: Round 3 Tag Team Bella Rossi, Mischa Brookes vs. Darling, Rilynn Rae
